" Section: Fix constant spelling mistakes {{{
" Go back to last misspelled word and pick first suggestion.
inoremap <F2> <Esc>[s1z=`]a

" Select last misspelled word (typing will edit).
nnoremap <F3> <Esc>[sve
inoremap <F3> <Esc>[sve
